=Episode 7=

18
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:45,630
Sungguh muncul lingkaran bintang lagi?

19
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,910
Mengenai kesepakatan kita sebelumnya…

20
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,270
