159
00:11:38,910 --> 00:11:40,350
Aku rasa itu sangat cantik,

160
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,030
sangat cantik.

161
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:50,030
Bunga yang berguguran
sama seperti kunang-kunang,

162
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:52,030
