163
00:11:52,790 --> 00:11:53,960
tidak pantas untuk dipikirkan.

164
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:56,710
Ya,

165
00:11:57,230 --> 00:11:58,350
Tuan Raja Naga.

166
00:11:59,550 --> 00:12:00,790
Aku lihat dalam drama,

167
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:02,710
di setiap hari pernikahan,

168
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,880
