♪Matamu memancarkan perubahan waktu
Tak bisa mengakhiri obsesi♪

205
00:16:15,230 --> 00:16:20,790
♪Menjadi perasaan yang tersisa♪

206
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:26,280
♪Jika hati mematahkan rasa rindu♪

207
00:16:26,590 --> 00:16:31,910
♪Enggan berpisah di kehidupan ini♪

208
00:16:32,110 --> 00:16:36,590
♪Setiap malam
Menerawang waktu seribu tahun♪

209
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:43,200
♪Menyelesaikan lukisan jodoh di tangan♪

210
00:16:43,470 --> 00:16:48,590
♪Jodoh yang dilukiskan oleh waktu♪

211
00:16:48,910 --> 00:16:53,140
♪Aku merindu di seumur hidupku ini♪

212
00:16:53,150 --> 00:16:54,030
(Maaf,)

213
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:55,960
(tubuh dan hatiku)

214
00:16:56,590 --> 00:16:58,200
(sudah kuberikan padanya.)

215
00:16:59,080 --> 00:17:04,800
♪Menebus keinginan di telapak tangan♪

216
00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:12,950
♪Perputaran kehidupan adalah jodoh♪

217
00:17:13,020 --> 00:17:16,820
(Kediaman Xiahou)

218
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:26,310
Liu Ying,

219
00:17:30,070 --> 00:17:31,190
ada apa denganmu akhir-akhir ini?

220
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:33,070
Kenapa kau selalu murung?

221
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:35,950
Aku tahu.

222
00:17:36,190 --> 00:17:37,950
Kau pasti diam-diam
membaca buku cerita lagi.

223
00:17:39,070 --> 00:17:41,470
Ya, aku sedang membaca buku cerita.

224
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:43,110
Lain kali tidak boleh membacanya lagi.

225
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:44,800
Oh, ya,

226
00:17:45,190 --> 00:17:46,830
